url: "https://github.com/IamRamgarhia/AdForge"
abstract: >
  AdForge is a browser-only, MIT-licensed AI advertising operations platform that
  replaces a stack of $49–$499/month SaaS marketing tools (Jasper, AdCreative,
  Anyword, Pencil, Marpipe) with a single open-source app. Users bring their own
  AI provider key — free tier (Groq, Cerebras, Gemini, OpenRouter) or paid
  (Claude, OpenAI, Mistral, DeepSeek) — and get 17 ad generators across Google,
  Meta, TikTok, YouTube, LinkedIn and X, plus 11 optimization tools (CTR
  optimizer, Quality Score improver, budget waste analyzer, ad fatigue detector,
  and more), competitor research, brand intelligence, content calendars, step-by-
  step launch guides for non-technical users, and a folder-portable data layer.
